## 1) Book Class 



### 1.1 isAvailable()

```
Function isAvailable()
     IF status = Available
          Return true
     Else 
          Return false
     Endif
End Function

```

***

### 1.2 borrow(memberID, today, loanDays)

```
Function borrow(memberID, today, loanDays)

     If status != Available
          Return false
     Endif

     status <- Borrowed
     borrowerId <- memberId
     dueDay <- today + loanDays

     Return true
End Function
```

