### 1.4 reserve(memberId, today)

```
Function reserve(memberId, today)

    if status = Borrowed AND borrowerId != memberId
        status <- reserved 
        reservedById <- memberId
        reservationExpiryDate <- today + 3
        return true
    endif
  
    return false
end Function
```

