### 3.4 returnBook(bookId, member)
```
Function returnBook(bookId, member)

    book <- Find book in books where book,Id = bookId
    if book not Found
        Display "Return denied: book not found."
        Return false
    endif

    if bookId not in member.borrowedBookIds
         Display "Return denied: Member did not borrow this book."
         Return false
    endif

    call book.returnbook()
    call member.removeBorrowed(bookId)

    Display "Return Successful"
    Return true
end Function
```

