### 3.6 overdueReport(today)
```
Function overdueReport(today)
   
    Display "Overdue Books:"
    for each book in books
        if book.isOverdue(today)
            Display book.id, book.title, book.borrowerId, book.DueDay
        endif
    endfor
end Function
```

