### 3.8 removeBook(bookId, librarian)
```
Function removeBook(bookId, librarian)

    book <- Find book in books where book.Id = bookId

    if book not found
        Display "Remove Denied: book not found"
        Return false 
    endif

    if book.status = Borrowed or book.status = Reserved
        Display "Remove Denied: book not found"
        Return false
    endif

    Remove book from books
    Display "Book removed Successfully"
    Return true

endFunction
```

